<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>World News, Today World News, Latest International News, World Breaking News, Trending News of World - Times of India</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>World News Today: Read the latest world news headlines, Current International breaking news world wide. In depth analysis and top news headlines world wide.</description><language>en-gb</language><lastBuildDate>2026-05-18T13:36:11+05:30</lastBuildDate><atom:link type="application/rss+xml" rel="self" href="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeeds/296589292.cms"/><copyright>Copyright:(C) Mon, 18 May 2026 13:36:11 IST Bennett Coleman &amp; Co. Ltd, http://in.indiatimes.com/policyterms/1554651.cms</copyright><docs>http://syndication.indiatimes.com/</docs><image><title>World News, Today World News, Latest International News, World Breaking News, Trending News of World - Times of India</title><url>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/507610.cms</url><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link></image><item><title><![CDATA[Strong earthquake hits southwest China, thousands evacuated after buildings damaged]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131169397.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[The Guangxi region of southwest China experienced a severe 5.2-magnitude earthquake, leaving its mark with structural damages and disruption to vital services. Thousands were forced to evacuate as the tremors rattled homes and offices alike. Tragically, authorities reported two lives lost and one individual unaccounted for, prompting active rescue missions.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/strong-earthquake-hits-southwest-china-thousands-evacuated-after-buildings-damaged/articleshow/131169397.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/strong-earthquake-hits-southwest-china-thousands-evacuated-after-buildings-damaged/articleshow/131169397.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-18T12:56:20+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131169820,imgsize-112602.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[‘I am calling from the police’: UK pensioners lose thousands in fake officer scam, authorities issue urgent warning]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131170177.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Elderly Britons are losing thousands to sophisticated scams where criminals pose as police and bank investigators. Victims are manipulated into revealing sensitive financial details or handing over bank cards to "couriers." Authorities urge extreme caution with unexpected calls involving money, emphasizing that genuine officials never request such information.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/i-am-calling-from-the-police-uk-pensioners-lose-thousands-in-fake-officer-scam-authorities-issue-urgent-warning/articleshow/131170177.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/i-am-calling-from-the-police-uk-pensioners-lose-thousands-in-fake-officer-scam-authorities-issue-urgent-warning/articleshow/131170177.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-18T13:13:47+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131170156,imgsize-28312.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[London tube strike confirmed after last-minute talks collapse, 4 days of disruption expected]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131169494.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[London faces significant travel disruption as RMT union members strike for four days over a proposed voluntary four-day working week for Tube drivers. Talks between Transport for London and the RMT failed, leading to planned walkouts from May 19-22, impacting services and causing potential overcrowding on alternative transport.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/london-tube-strike-confirmed-after-last-minute-talks-collapse-4-days-of-disruption-expected/articleshow/131169494.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/london-tube-strike-confirmed-after-last-minute-talks-collapse-4-days-of-disruption-expected/articleshow/131169494.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-18T12:46:30+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131169588,imgsize-291600.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[‘World inside water’: Danish farmer built an entire world map inside a lake]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131169449.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/world-inside-water-danish-farmer-built-an-entire-world-map-inside-a-lake/articleshow/131169449.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/world-inside-water-danish-farmer-built-an-entire-world-map-inside-a-lake/articleshow/131169449.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-18T12:44:14+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131169552,imgsize-1639248.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[‘Woke mind virus killed my son’: Elon Musk sharply condemns child’s gender transitio