36+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131165236,imgsize-63952.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Iran helping Cuba? US intel flags ‘growing threat’ over drone build-up amid Havana tensions]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131164702.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[US intelligence suggests Cuba has acquired over 300 military drones, raising security concerns about potential attacks on American targets like Guantanamo Bay and Key West. CIA chief visited Havana, warning against hostilities and urging an end to its "totalitarian government." Cuba denies threatening war, asserting its right to self-defense amid growing defense ties with Russia and Iran.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/defence/international/iran-helping-cuba-us-intelligence-flags-growing-threat-over-drone-build-up-amid-havana-tensions-report/articleshow/131164702.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/defence/international/iran-helping-cuba-us-intelligence-flags-growing-threat-over-drone-build-up-amid-havana-tensions-report/articleshow/131164702.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-18T08:00:34+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131165593,imgsize-1361642.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Faced with war, crackdown against Baha’is rising in Iran]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131164635.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/faced-with-war-crackdown-against-bahais-rising-in-iran/articleshow/131164635.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/faced-with-war-crackdown-against-bahais-rising-in-iran/articleshow/131164635.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-18T07:44:11+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Rudroneel Ghosh</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131164658,imgsize-1616636.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Trump-Xi summit: Taiwan absent from White House China visit summary amid Iran, trade focus]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131164281.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[US President Trump's China visit yielded trade and investment pacts, including Boeing aircraft and agricultural deals. Both nations agreed on Iran's nuclear non-proliferation and Strait of Hormuz access. Notably, Taiwan, a key discussion point, was omitted from the White House fact sheet, despite Trump hinting at reconsidering arms sales.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-xi-jinping-summit-taiwan-absent-from-white-house-china-visit-summary-amid-iran-trade-focus/articleshow/131164281.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-xi-jinping-summit-taiwan-absent-from-white-house-china-visit-summary-amid-iran-trade-focus/articleshow/131164281.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-18T07:11:23+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131164362,imgsize-1122685.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Police launch probe after fatal robbery attack in UK's East Belfast]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131159398.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A man, identified as Nicholas Gordon, has died after being severely injured during a robbery in an East Belfast apartment building. Police were alerted to the incident, which occurred around 4:45 AM, and have charged two individuals with aggravated burglary. The community has expressed alarm and distress over the violent crime.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/police-launch-probe-after-fatal-robbery-attack-in-uks-east-belfast/articleshow/131159398.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/police-launch-probe-after-fatal-robbery-attack-in-uks-east-belfast/articleshow/131159398.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-17T22:56:57+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131159403,imgsize-8836.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[No laughing matter: Colbert exit sparks fears for political satire in America]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131158886.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/no-laughing-matter-colbert-exit-sparks-fears-for-political-satire-in-america/articleshow/131158886.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/no-laughing-matter-colbert-exit-sparks-fears-for-political-satire-in-america/articleshow/131158886.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-17T22:33:57+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Chidanand Rajghatta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131158958,imgsize-70832.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Backyard snake now a noose? Back-to-back attacks tarnish Pak army’s reputation]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.ind