n in Birmingham, an incident linked to the removal of flags. The victim, in his 30s, sustained broken legs requiring surgery. Police detained a 44-year-old man in London, who will be questioned regarding the collision and subsequent flight from the scene.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/london-man-held-after-van-injures-pedestrian-during-protests-over-removal-of-flags-in-birmingham/articleshow/131156845.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/london-man-held-after-van-injures-pedestrian-during-protests-over-removal-of-flags-in-birmingham/articleshow/131156845.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-17T20:42:50+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131156936,imgsize-44322.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[UK healthcare expansion: Steve Jobs son Reed Jobs plans to invest in cancer startups]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131156119.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-healthcare-expansion-steve-jobs-son-reed-jobs-plans-to-invest-in-cancer-startups/articleshow/131156119.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-healthcare-expansion-steve-jobs-son-reed-jobs-plans-to-invest-in-cancer-startups/articleshow/131156119.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-17T20:32:08+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131156742,imgsize-945941.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[From uranium transfer to frozen assets, US sets 5 conditions in response to Iran’s proposal]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;marg